    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/c2390155c446f623912fbf81e2c0176e.poster.avif?t=1770723654\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/c2390155c446f623912fbf81e2c0176e.webm?t=1770723654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/c2390155c446f623912fbf81e2c0176e.mp4?t=1770723654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《LIVING HELL》是一款支持 1–4 人的线上合作恐怖游戏，背景设定在佩利坎市。臭氧层的崩溃造成了灾难性后果，太阳辐射引发了大范围的恐怖变异。作为研究团队的一员，你必须在夜晚进入城市，为政府的研究 AI——DAWN-4o 收集样本。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">带回样本</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/f0c7e025924c44ff6c65602b58c8509c.poster.avif?t=1770723654\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/f0c7e025924c44ff6c65602b58c8509c.webm?t=1770723654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/f0c7e025924c44ff6c65602b58c8509c.mp4?t=1770723654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>将变异样本交给 DAWN-4o，为她的研究提供能量，以确保你能继续生存。每个阶段都能帮助她学习和适应，解锁新的蓝图和升级。不遵守要求意味着你的庇护所将失去电力。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">不要信任任何人</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/ff906518a65605dbde6dd35fe19477e0.poster.avif?t=1770723654\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/ff906518a65605dbde6dd35fe19477e0.webm?t=1770723654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/ff906518a65605dbde6dd35fe19477e0.mp4?t=1770723654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在佩利坎市探索时，你将直面那些被扭曲成人间噩梦的人类与动物。他们难以预测的行为会让你时刻紧张不安。记住：没有人能免疫辐射的变异效应。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">与太阳赛跑</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/c15336a334b20fa3590bf594f52c0acb.poster.avif?t=1770723654\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/c15336a334b20fa3590bf594f52c0acb.webm?t=1770723654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/c15336a334b20fa3590bf594f52c0acb.mp4?t=1770723654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在夜间搜寻关键物资，同时通过补水来管理你的“热负荷”。必须在日出前逃回庇护所，否则将被炽烈的太阳辐射吞噬。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">探索佩利坎市</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/cbdebf2edabf76f659a7445928ebc518.poster.avif?t=1770723654\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/cbdebf2edabf76f659a7445928ebc518.webm?t=1770723654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/cbdebf2edabf76f659a7445928ebc518.mp4?t=1770723654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>乘坐地铁前往精心打造的城区，每个城区都有多个建筑内部与不同的布局，每一次探索都不相同。沉浸在这座曾经繁荣，如今只剩焦黑废墟的现代城市里，危险在每个角落潜伏。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">一起，还是独自上路</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/8a35e83365aa153e79360981bccbdb28.poster.avif?t=1770723654\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/8a35e83365aa153e79360981bccbdb28.webm?t=1770723654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/8a35e83365aa153e79360981bccbdb28.mp4?t=1770723654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>可从 8 名拥有独特被动能力的可玩角色中选择。支持临近语音、对讲机、共享储物以及永久存档。想挑战极限？也可以在离线单人模式中独自冒险。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">搜寻与制作</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/8615c372a4de49f629600a8d5d145f4b.poster.avif?t=1770723654\" width=1170 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/8615c372a4de49f629600a8d5d145f4b.webm?t=1770723654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078760/extras/8615c372a4de49f629600a8d5d145f4b.mp4?t=1770723654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>收集材料来制作武器、工具和消耗品，确保你和你的队友能活下去。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 六个精心设计的城区，每次探索时建筑内部布局都会发生变化<br></li><li>八位拥有独特被动技能的可玩角色<br></li><li>超过十几种行为各异的变异生物<br></li><li>受经典生存恐怖启发的制作与背包系统<br></li><li>沉浸式临近语音聊天并带有口型同步<br></li><li>支持跨局的永久存档<br></li><li>完整的手柄与 Steam Deck 支持<br></li><li>复古风格视觉与现代渲染技术相结合，带来高性能的沉浸式体验<br></li><li> 客户端预测与延迟补偿网络系统，保证流畅战斗<br></li><li>由 Phoenix Glendinning 创作的原创配乐</li></ul>",
